title: Lakers, Duke, Josh Rosen, and the Raiders
itunes:title: Lakers, Duke, Josh Rosen, and the Raiders
description:
Filling in for Colin, Doug Gottlieb talks about when it was the beginning of the end for the Los Angeles Lakers, why people don't hate Duke right now, the treatment of Arizona Cardinals QB Josh Rosen, and why the Oakland Raiders were smart to trade Khalil Mack. Guests include Mark Schlereth, Evan Daniels, Cuttino Mobley, and Dahntay Jones.
